{
  "an1.188:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 ",
  "an1.188:0.2": "14. Paṭhamavagga ",
  "an1.188-197:1.1": "\"Etadaggaṁ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṁ bhikkhūnaṁ rattaññūnaṁ yadidaṁ aññāsikoṇḍañño.\n(1)",
  "an1.188-197:1.2": "…   Mahāpaññānaṁ yadidaṁ sāriputto.\n(2)",
  "an1.188-197:2.1": "",
  "an1.188-197:2.2": "…   Iddhimantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahāmoggallāno.\n(3)",
  "an1.188-197:2.3": "…   Dhutavādānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākassapo.\n(4)",
  "an1.188-197:2.4": "…   Dibbacakkhukānaṁ yadidaṁ anuruddho.\n(5)",
  "an1.188-197:2.5": "…   Uccākulikānaṁ yadidaṁ bhaddiyo kāḷigodhāya putto.\n(6)",
  "an1.188-197:2.6": "…   Mañjussarānaṁ yadidaṁ lakuṇḍaka bhaddiyo.\n(7)",
  "an1.188-197:2.7": "…   Sīhanādikānaṁ yadidaṁ piṇḍolabhāradvājo.\n(8)",
  "an1.188-197:2.8": "…   Dhammakathikānaṁ yadidaṁ puṇṇo mantāṇiputto.\n(9)",
  "an1.188-197:2.9": "…   Saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṁ vibhajantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākaccāno\"ti.\n(10)\nVaggo paṭhamo.\nPaṭhamavagga"
}